# This directory is kept in git to track experiment logs

Logs are organized as: logs/{generator}/{lamp_num}/{retriever}/

Example structure:
- logs/flanT5Small/lamp1/bm25/alpha_1.log
- logs/flanT5Small/lamp1/bm25/alpha_1_normalize.log

The logs directory complements experiment_results/ by:
1. Storing persistent records of all experiment runs (committed to git)
2. Tracking configuration, progress, and performance metrics
3. Enabling easy debugging if experiments are interrupted

Large result files (.json) are kept in experiment_results/ only (not in git).
